{"tid":2253662,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳陳月內離安全屋 管浩鳴稱不知","createTime":"2020-10-22T10:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T10:18:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"57dde1e64e14e357e8c49d48aecad091fa239147","tid":2253662,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:03:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201022/2GNO4GYVF5ARXIP7R65N5BDOCI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201022%2F2GNO4GYVF5ARXIP7R65N5BDOCI%2F&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPUyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=e1cb1eda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201022%2F2GNO4GYVF5ARXIP7R65N5BDOCI%2F&h=25584a97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201022/2GNO4GYVF5ARXIP7R65N5BDOCI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n傳陳月內離安全屋 管浩鳴稱不知<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5IMIptx4qp3iFajcM7298caxxsk=/6186x4163/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BUMMWJLA4VFFPB5HPJLTGPPI6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5IMIptx4qp3iFajcM7298caxxsk%3D%2F6186x4163%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBUMMWJLA4VFFPB5HPJLTGPPI6M.jpg&h=20610fdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n管浩鳴<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】涉嫌在台殺死女友潘曉穎後潛逃回港的陳同佳，去年就洗黑錢案服刑，明日出獄滿一年，亦是潘媽媽要求他赴台投案期限，惟他仍出發赴台無期。昨有報道指港府擬在未來一、兩個月安排陳同佳離開警方安全屋，但一直協助陳同佳的牧師管浩鳴卻指不清楚安排，但認為目前最重要是解決陳的赴台手續。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：張建宗晤德領事 反對庇中大女生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指先要解決赴台手續<br />\n<br />\n繼潘媽媽前日往政府總部向保安局長李家超第二度發公開信，要求當局盡快讓陳同佳離開安全屋，早日辦理赴台簽證後，親政府報章《星島日報》昨發表評論文章，聲稱「據聞，當局已開始安排讓陳同佳離開安全屋的計劃，預。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。管稱：「如果有需要他（陳同佳）自己去的話，當然會去，但我暫時沒有收到訊息通知要他自己去。」潘媽媽則表示，對陳同佳可能離開安全屋的說法暫不作回應。"},{"pid":"df15f8237a2f1f9ae46fce9f5a25e117ff620f15","tid":2253662,"uid":33174,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:07:08.000Z","msg":"一早應該釋放陳同佳 <br />\n唔放佢出去潘曉穎老母點尋仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526e0e515ec06f4ec1da7657b167b6625a47154a","tid":2253662,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:07:14.000Z","msg":"豪宅太悶住不了人 陳同佳證實了這清息..."},{"pid":"740a942e56ce25d117cfa88bc7a0faed41db5c66","tid":2253662,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df15f8237a2f1f9ae46fce9f5a25e117ff620f15","tid":2253662,"uid":33174,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:07:08.000Z","msg":"一早應該釋放陳同佳 <br />\n唔放佢出去潘曉穎老母點尋仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:08:38.000Z","msg":"寫信定要求對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8e2136e54304d87266e2d1e8267c01338c10fa","tid":2253662,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"740a942e56ce25d117cfa88bc7a0faed41db5c66","tid":2253662,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df15f8237a2f1f9ae46fce9f5a25e117ff620f15","tid":2253662,"uid":33174,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:07:08.000Z","msg":"一早應該釋放陳同佳 <br />\n唔放佢出去潘曉穎老母點尋仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:08:38.000Z","msg":"寫信定要求對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地無左後代 要佢負起責任 同潘老母結婚生仔"},{"pid":"4e6224733f02a26035782774cb760b2a51e97961","tid":2253662,"uid":234553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc8e2136e54304d87266e2d1e8267c01338c10fa","tid":2253662,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"740a942e56ce25d117cfa88bc7a0faed41db5c66","tid":2253662,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df15f8237a2f1f9ae46fce9f5a25e117ff620f15","t